top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Uber guilds</span><hr size=1> Throw in a few Vindicators around the world.  Drops only one quite ok but not uber item (no mudflation), takes some organization to kill, yet can be done in a couple hours even for a casual guild.  Repops quickly, just like Vindicator.  The satisfaction of killing Vindicator for a casual guild is very high.<br>
<br>
Is there's too much Vindicator loot entering the world?  Doubt it.  Is Vindicator up most of the time?  Yes.  Is he fun to kill?  Yes.  Does it take an uber guild to kill him?  No.  My guild is far from uber, yet we kill him whenever we want (i.e. when nothing more rewarding is up).<br>
<br>
Just add some Vindi's in SS, Thurgadin, GD and, say, Chardok.<br>
<br>
